import React from 'react' import Homes from '../Homes' import { Link } from 'react-router-dom'; const ListingCards = () => { return (
{Homes.map(home => (
realestate application | {home.listing_status} |

${home.price}

{home.location} | {home.address}

Bed: {home.bedrooms} | Bath: {home.bath} | {home.footage} Sq Ft | {home.lot_size} Acre(s)

))}
) } export default ListingCards
